snippet.title: Tales of Seikyu - Official Gameplay Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Explore a fantasy land, manage your farm, and transform into animals in Tales of Seikyu.

Tales of Seikyu is coming soon to PC.
